metadata.name: Catfishing
metadata.description:
Catfishing is a work of denunciation, but also of revendication.  
In the NFT world scams and scams are always lurking, like poison that drop after drop can ruin the water more clear.  
These impostors who like a swarm always lurking around you buzzing.  
This work helped me to emerge from the depths in which I was stranded.
